<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Reschedule Request</title>
</head>

<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background:#f3f4f6; font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#374151;">

<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="padding:24px;">
<tr>
<td align="center">

<table role="presentation" width="600" style="background:#fff; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:8px;">

  <!-- Subject -->
  <tr>
    <td style="padding:30px 24px 10px;">
      <p style="margin:0;">
        Email Subject: 
        <strong>Reschedule Request - Krost Appointment</strong>
      </p>
    </td>
  </tr>

  <!-- Body -->
  <tr>
    <td style="padding:0px 24px 30px 24px; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6; color:#374151;">

      <p>Hi <strong>{{ salesperson_name }}</strong>,</p>

      <p>
        Please accept my apologies, but due to an unexpected change in our schedule, 
        I am no longer able to meet at our originally scheduled time on 
        <strong>{{ original_date }}</strong>.
      </p>

      <p>
        I would love to find a new time that works better for you.
      </p>

      <p>
        To keep things simple, you can view my live availability and select a new slot directly via the link below:
      </p>

    </td>
  </tr>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <tr>
    <td align="center" style="padding:20px;">
      <a href="{{ reschedule_link }}"
         style="background:#255793; color:#fff; padding:12px 24px; text-decoration:none; border-radius:6px; display:inline-block;">
        Click here to Reschedule Your Appointment
      </a>
    </td>
  </tr>

  <!-- Extra -->
  <tr>
    <td style="padding:0 24px 24px; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6; color:#374151;">

      <p>
        Once you pick a new time, you will receive an updated confirmation and calendar invite immediately.
      </p>

      <p>
        I look forward to meeting with you and discussing your project soon.
      </p>

      <p>
        Thank you for your understanding.
      </p>

      <p style="margin-top:20px;">
        Best regards,<br>
        <strong>{{ salesperson_name }}</strong>
      </p>

    </td>
  </tr>

</table>

</td>
</tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>